class StereoBM\(Stereo\)\:

 def _to_3d\(self\, disp\, color_frame_l\)\:
 points \= super\(\)\._to_3d\(disp\, color_frame_l\)
 mask \= disp \> disp\.min\(\)

 out_points \= points\[mask\]
 out_colors \= color_frame_l\[mask\]

 def __init__\(self\, w\, h\, focal_length\)\:
 super\(\)\.__init__\(h\, w\, focal_length\, "StereoBM disparity"\)

 self\.stereo \= cv2\.StereoBM_create\(16\, 5\) \# best between the options 0\,5 or 16\,5

 cv2\.namedWindow\(super\(\)\.window_name\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("numDisparities"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 1\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("blockSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 5\, 255\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.setTrackbarMin\("blockSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 5\)

 def __change\(self\, x\)\:
 print\(x\)

 block_size \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("blockSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)
 if block_size \% 2 \=\= 0\:
 block_size \+\= 1
 cv2\.setTrackbarPos\("blockSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, block_size\)

 num_disparities \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("numDisparities"\, super\(\)\.window_name\) \* 16

 self\.stereo \= cv2\.StereoBM_create\(num_disparities\, block_size\)

 def compute\(self\, frame_l\, frame_r\)\:
 frame_l \= cv2\.cvtColor\(frame_l\, cv2\.COLOR_BGR2GRAY\)
 frame_r \= cv2\.cvtColor\(frame_r\, cv2\.COLOR_BGR2GRAY\)

 disp \= self\.stereo\.compute\(frame_l\, frame_r\)

 norm_coeff \= 255 / disp\.max\(\)
 cv2\.imshow\(super\(\)\.window_name\, disp \* norm_coeff / 255\)

 return disp


class StereoSGBM\(Stereo\)\:
 def compute\(self\, frame_l\, frame_r\)\:
 disp \= self\.stereo\.compute\(frame_l\, frame_r\)\.astype\(np\.float32\) / 16\.0

 min_disparity \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("minDisparity"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)
 numDisparity \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("numDisparity"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 disparity \= \(disp \- min_disparity\) / numDisparity
 cv2\.imshow\(super\(\)\.window_name\, disparity\)

 return disp

 def __init__\(self\, w\, h\, focal_length\)\:
 super\(\)\.__init__\(w\, h\, focal_length\, "StereoSGBM disparity"\)

 window_size \= 3
 min_disp \= 16
 num_disp \= 112 \- min_disp
 self\.stereo \= cv2\.StereoSGBM_create\(minDisparity\=min_disp\,
 numDisparities\=num_disp\,
 uniquenessRatio\=10\,
 speckleWindowSize\=100\,
 speckleRange\=32\,
 disp12MaxDiff\=1\,
 P1\=8 \* 3 \* window_size \*\* 2\,
 P2\=32 \* 3 \* window_size \*\* 2\,
 \)

 cv2\.namedWindow\(super\(\)\.window_name\)

 cv2\.createTrackbar\("minDisparity"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, min_disp\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("numDisparities"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, num_disp\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("uniquenessRatio"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 0\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("speckleWindowSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 0\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("speckleRange"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 0\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("disp12MaxDiff"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 0\, 20\, self\.__change\)
 cv2\.createTrackbar\("window_size"\, super\(\)\.window_name\, 0\, 20\, self\.__change\)

 def _to_3d\(self\, disp\, color_frame_l\)\:
 pass

 def __change\(self\, x\)\:
 min_disparity \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("minDisparity"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 numDisparity \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("numDisparity"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 uniquenessRatio \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("uniquenessRatio"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 speckleWindowSize \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("speckleWindowSize"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 speckleRange \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("speckleRange"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 disp12MaxDiff \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("disp12MaxDiff"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 window_size \= cv2\.getTrackbarPos\("window_size"\, super\(\)\.window_name\)

 self\.stereo \= cv2\.StereoSGBM_create\(minDisparity\=min_disparity\,
 numDisparities\=numDisparity\,
 uniquenessRatio\=uniquenessRatio\,
 speckleWindowSize\=speckleWindowSize\,
 speckleRange\=speckleRange\,
 disp12MaxDiff\=disp12MaxDiff\,
 P1\=8 \* 3 \* window_size \*\* 2\,
 P2\=32 \* 3 \* window_size \*\* 2\)
